<div class="about-page">
    <h1>About SnipShare</h1>

    <p>SnipShare is a minimalist code snippet sharing platform built for developers who want to share code quickly without the hassle of creating accounts.</p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>No account required</li>
        <li>Syntax highlighting for popular languages</li>
        <li>Clean, distraction-free interface</li>
        <li>Expiration options for temporary snippets</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Node.js + Express</li>
        <li>SQLite for storage</li>
        <li>EJS templates</li>
        <li>Vanilla JavaScript</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>We don't track users or collect personal data. Your snippets are stored with minimal metadata.</p>
